description:
This property has something for everyone! if you love entertaining your guests then this is the property for you. With your undercover outdoor entertainment area and indoor barbeque area, your guests will never want to leave. There is plenty of space left for the kids to play or for the family pet to run around. Don't forget the HUGE 3-car backyard shed that is perfect to store your boat or cars for that extra peace of mind.

This property screams CONVENIENCE, CONVENIENCE, CONVENIENCE! Enjoy your weekends by taking a short walk to the end of the street to Glenrock Park for the kids to play, watch the latest movies at Reading Cinemas, or enjoy some bowling or arcade games at Cannon Park only 6 minutes away! School dropoff can be a breeze with Thuringowa State High School only 5 minutes away and Little Zebras Childcare Centre just 4 minutes away.

What more could you ask for when this property has:
- 3 spacious bedrooms, enough space for everyone!
- A modern and well-kept bathroom that gives you the option of a shower or a bath.
- Family-style kitchen with ample cupboard space and modern appliances.
- Fully airconditioned throughout for year-round comfort.
- No carpeted floors, easy to maintain!
- Indoor barbeque area with plenty of bench space and easy access through the outdoor servery.
- HUGE backyard shed can fit 3 vehicles and has plenty of undercover space!
- Undercover entertaining area, perfect for gatherings.
- Study benches installed in 2 bedrooms, great for the kids!
- Single garage access from the front yard.
- Side access to the property, perfect for boat access!
- Solar panels, to keep your energy bills low.

This property is ready to go to its new owner!
Place your offer today! All offers will e submitted to the owner.
This property is a must to inspect! Call now for an immediate inspection.
